pe.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Metody</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\">Metoda <code><strong>toLocaleString()</strong></code> zwraca łańcuch znaków reprezentujący wszystkie elementy w tablicy. Każdy element jest konwerterowany do &nbsp;łańcucha znaku&nbsp;za pomocą lokalnych wywołań&nbsp;<code>toLocaleString. Elementy&nbsp;</code>łaczone są separatorem zdefiniowanym dla lokalnego języka (np. przecinek).</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"składnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>arr</var>.toLocaleString();</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opis","title":"Opis","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Poniższe elementy tablic są konwertowane na łańcuchy znaków za pomocą wbudowanych metod&nbsp;<code>toLocaleString</code></p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>Object</code>: <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li>\n <li><code>Number</code>: <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/toLocaleString\"><code>Number.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li>\n <li><code>Date</code>: <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toLocaleString\"><code>Date.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykład","title":"Przykład","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"użycie_tolocalestring","title":"Użycie&nbsp;<code>toLocaleString</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">let numer = 1337;\nlet data = new Date();\nlet tablica = [numer , data, 'foo'];\n\nlet str = tablica.toLocaleString();\n\nconsole.log(str);\n// logs '1337,19.11.2020, 17:21:06,foo'\n// if run in a Polish (pl-PL) locale with timezone Europe/Warsaw\n\n\nlet strEn = tablica.toLocaleString(\"en-US\");  // \"1,337,11/19/2020, 5:21:06 PM,foo\"</pre>","titleAsText":"Użycie toLocaleString"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specyfikacja</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Komentarze</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/publications/files/ECMA-ST-ARCH/ECMA-262,%203rd%20edition,%20December%201999.pdf\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'ECMAScript 3rd Edition (ECMA-262)' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 3rd Edition (ECMA-262)</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Inicjalna definicja</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.2.4.3\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'Array.prototype.toLocaleString' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-array.pr